      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "I'M ALRIGHT (7) was a last start winner this course and distance taking a Grade 5 in 15.70 in the best time on the card and clocking a personal best as well. Expected to go close again if runs up to latest. MY WEE LASS (4) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing seventh (16.44) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Form at the trip sound including two wins. One of the main contenders. FASCINATE DEBRA (5) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (15.76) at this track behind Miss Arizona in a Grade 4/5. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. Leading chance. WOW PARTY TIME (2) cannot be left out after leading and holding on for a placing last start.",
